        Invocation Result:

        Operation Errors:

        public Install.StartInvocation start(InstallTypes.InstallSpec spec)
        Description copied from interface: Install
        Start the appliance installation. This method was added in vSphere API 6.7.

        Operation Errors:
        Unauthenticated - if the caller is not authenticated.
        Unauthenticated - if the partner PSC credentials are not valid when configuring PSC to replicate with partner PSC.
        Unauthenticated - if external PSC credentials are not valid when configuring a VCSA_EXTERNAL appliance.
        InvalidArgument - if passed arguments are invalid.
        NotAllowedInCurrentState - if the appliance is not in INITIALIZED state.

        Specified by:

        Unauthenticated - if the caller is not authenticated.
